column16: Jaff Decker flies out to center fielder Adam Jones.
Desmond Jennings walks.   Logan Morrison to 2nd.
Brad Miller flies out to right fielder Joey Rickard.
Logan Morrison singles on a line drive to center fielder Adam Jones.
Xander Bogaerts flies out to right fielder Joey Rickard.
Dustin Pedroia called out on strikes.
Mookie Betts grounds out, second baseman Jonathan Schoop to first baseman Chris Davis.
Blake Swihart singles on a line drive to left fielder Hyun Soo Kim.   Travis Shaw to 2nd.
Jackie Bradley Jr.   flies out to left fielder Hyun Soo Kim in foul territory.
David Ortiz homers (14) on a fly ball to right field.
Orioles challenged (tag play), call on the field was overturned: With David Ortiz batting, Xander Bogaerts caught stealing 2nd base, catcher Caleb Joseph to shortstop Manny Machado.
Michael Martinez grounds into a force out, shortstop Paul Janish to second baseman Jonathan Schoop.   Juan Uribe out at 2nd.
Yan Gomes called out on strikes.
Juan Uribe singles on a line drive to right fielder Nolan Reimold.   Jose Ramirez to 2nd.
Jose Ramirez singles on a ground ball to right fielder Nolan Reimold.   Francisco Lindor scores.
Mike Napoli flies out to center fielder Joey Rickard.   Francisco Lindor to 3rd.
Francisco Lindor reaches on a throwing error by pitcher Ashur Tolliver.   Francisco Lindor to 2nd.
Jason Castro called out on strikes.
Evan Gattis grounds out, shortstop Manny Machado to first baseman Chris Davis.
